oll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>r</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>, respectively, from the center of the inner wire, as shown. Which of the following are the correct expressions for the magnetic field <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B sub P\"><math alttext=\"B sub P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> at point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"P\"><math alttext=\"P\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>P</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and the magnetic field <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"B sub Q\"><math alttext=\"B sub Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>B</mi></mrow><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> at point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Q\"><math alttext=\"Q\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mtext>Q</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>?</p>\n",
